response.original_title: The Death of Vince Foster: What Really Happened?
response.overview: What really happened to White House counsel Vince Foster on 20 July, 1993? Suicide or murder? The documentary explores several evidences that indicates a foul play could have happened and high officials linked to Clinton administration were responsible for a lousy investigation filled with inconsistencies, leaving room to countless conjectures and alternative theories.
response.title: The Death of Vince Foster: What Really Happened?
